to me with a smile...

1064
01:13:01,477 --> 01:13:09,043
and would spark my desire
with your love...

1065
01:13:09,418 --> 01:13:17,257
l looked for you in the
breeze which caresses me...

1066
01:13:17,459 --> 01:13:25,230
l stood on the shores
waiting for you...

1067
01:13:25,434 --> 01:13:43,376
