you are Uday.

1085
01:16:47,402 --> 01:16:48,232
Yes.

1086
01:16:48,503 --> 01:16:52,439
lf she had mentioned your name,
you must be very special.

1087
01:16:52,874 --> 01:16:54,273
Will you give her these papers?

