- Please sit.

1106
01:18:54,396 --> 01:18:56,455
Where is my uncle?
- He is giving treatment.

1107
01:18:56,665 --> 01:18:57,188
He will be here in 10 minutes.

1108
01:18:57,399 --> 01:19:00,368
