she saw blood in her hand.

1171
01:24:52,620 --> 01:24:54,952
lf she knows this...
- Don't tell her.

1172
01:24:55,290 --> 01:24:58,123
Give her this medicine regularly.
Tell her this is for strength.

1173
01:25:00,862 --> 01:25:02,090
