01:48:14,354 --> 01:48:17,915
lt's not something to be prompted,
you must feel it.

1434
01:48:26,800 --> 01:48:27,596
l'm feeling very much.

1435
01:48:27,801 --> 01:48:30,269
My feeling is mine and
your feeling is yours.

1436
01:48:42,482 --> 01:48:44,109
