1744
02:11:58,210 --> 02:11:59,677
l'll also jump.

1745
02:11:59,878 --> 02:12:01,345
Eatery owner is no ordinary man.

1746
02:12:01,613 --> 02:12:02,841
He'll gun down us.

1747
02:12:03,215 --> 02:12:06,013
